\c 47
\s Marudzi ose ngaarumbidze Jehovha
\d Kumutungamiriri wekuimba. Pisarema revanakomana vaKora.
\p
\v 1 Uchirai, imwi marudzi ose! Pururudzai kuna Mwari neinzwi remufaro.
\v 2 Nokuti Jehovha Wekumusoro-soro anotyisa; ndiMambo mukuru pamusoro penyika yose.
\v 3 Achaisa vanhu pasi pedu, nemarudzi pasi petsoka dzedu.
\v 4 Achatisarudzira nhaka yedu, ruremekedzo rwaJakove waanoda. Sera.
\p
\v 5 Mwari wakwira nekudanidzira, Jehovha nekurira kwehwamanda.
\v 6 Imbirai Mwari rumbidzo, imbai rumbidzo; imbirai mambo wedu rumbidzo, imbai rumbidzo.
\v 7 Nokuti Mwari ndiMambo wepasi pose; imbai rumbidzo \add ne\add*kunzwisisa.
\v 8 Mwari anotonga pamusoro pevahedheni; Mwari agere pachigaro cheushe cheutsvene hwake.
\v 9 Machinda evanhu aungana pamwe, vanhu vaMwari waAbhurahama. Nokuti nhovo dzepanyika ndedzaMwari; wakakwiridzirwa kwazvo.
